OL,5,EGOING CHRISTMAS CRACKERS? W|}~t m5j~ 
OL,7,BPlanning to have fun with the family   
OL,8,Bthis Christmas? Or are youEdreading    
OL,9,Bbeing stuck in the house for days with 
OL,10,BAuntie Flo and mounds of mince pies?   
OL,12,BStress levels rise dramatically over   
OL,13,Bthe festive season as a result of      
OL,14,Bfamily tensions and it's the busiest   
OL,15,Btime of year forEThe Samaritans.       
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,BLast year calls to the helpline rose by
OL,18,E17%Bin Christmas week and went up a    
OL,19,BfurtherE9%Bduring New Year.            
