OL,5,EGOING CHRISTMAS CRACKERS? W|}~t m5j~ 
OL,6,                            Q           
OL,7,EThe SamaritansBare preparing for       
OL,8,Banother deluge of calls from people    
OL,9,Bunable to cope with the stresses of    
OL,10,BChristmasEwith the family.             
OL,12,B"Many people find it hard to cope with 
OL,13,Bthe pressure of expecting to have fun  
OL,14,B- it's all the moreEpoignantBwhen they 
OL,15,Bdon't," says spokesmanEJustin Irwin.   
OL,16,B                                       
OL,17,B"It's good to express your emotions but
OL,18,Bmany find it hard to do that with      
OL,19,Bfamilies. That's why they call us."    
