OL,5,EGOING CHRISTMAS CRACKERS? W|}~t m5j~ 
OL,7,BTheEMental Health FoundationBis issuing
OL,8,Badvice to help people survive the      
OL,9,Btensions of a family Christmas.        
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BThe charity has drawn up aEfive-point  
OL,12,EplanBto help people cope. These are:   
OL,14,EBSet tasks forBeach family member     
OL,15,EBDiscuss potential problems in advance
OL,16,EBTake time out away from the family   
OL,17,EBSet a strict financial budget        
OL,18,EBDon't over-indulge in food and drink.
